CGI::Lite v2.04
----------------

Released: 4th Jul 2014


DESCRIPTION
-----------

You can use this module to decode form and query information, including file
uploads, as well as cookies in a very simple manner; you need not concern
yourself with the actual details behind the decoding process.


NEW IN THIS VERSION
-------------------

Only documentation changes since 2.03_02.

The uploads have had a bug fix since 2.03 which should allow successful
binary uploads for MS Windows servers.

See the CHANGES file for full history.

$Id: README,v 1.5 2014/07/04 11:23:37 pete Exp $
